you were discreet and left no trace.

33
00:02:57.010 --> 00:03:01.598
Well. in normal circumstances. yes.
That is exactly what I do.

34
00:03:02.349 --> 00:03:06.561
Unfortunately.
there was a confluence of events...

35
00:03:06.562 --> 00:03:07.980
What did I pay you for?

36
00:03:10.524 --> 00:03:11.524
A hit.

37
00:03:12.359 --> 00:03:16.445
To look like an accident
in the Westacres parking lot.

38
00:03:16.446 --> 00:03:17.780
You blew it up.

39
00:03:17.781 --> 00:03:20.908
No. I did not.
That was part of the problem.

40
00:03:20.909 --> 00:03:24.203
