71
00:04:52.835 --> 00:04:53.836
Sure.

72
00:04:54.837 --> 00:04:58.715
<i>I'll bring the old fucks back here
and chop 'em up myself.</i>

73
00:06:12.664 --> 00:06:13.706
Shit.

74
00:06:13.707 --> 00:06:14.874
Dogs. Fuck.

75
00:06:14.875 --> 00:06:16.001
What do they want?

76
00:06:16.668 --> 00:06:19.379
Me probably. I keep
dicking their boss around.

77
00:06:20.506 --> 00:06:22.925
Jump on the phone
and see if they're in the building.

78
00:06:29.306 --> 00:06:30.806
<i>Have they come in?</i>

79
